text: Yevgeniya Voloshenko (born 3 April 1979) is a Kazakhstani cross-country skier. She competed in three events at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Kazakhstan Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kokshetau
